\c 26
\p
\v 1 Sezvakaita chando muzhizha, uye sezvakaita mvura mukucheka, Saizvozvo kukudzwa hakufaniri benzi.
\v 2 Sezvinoita shiri pakupaparika kwayo, nenyenganyenga pakubhururuka kwayo, Saizvozvo kutuka pasina mhosva hakuitiki.
\v 3 Tyava yakaitirwa bhiza, namatomu mbongoro, Neshamhu musana wamapenzi.
\v 4 Usapindura benzi noupenzi hwaro, Kuti urege kufanana naro.
\v 5 Pindura benzi noupenzi hwaro, Kuti rirege kuti rakachenjera.
\v 6 Anotuma shoko noruoko rwebenzi, Unozvigura tsoka, nokunwa kutambudzika.
\v 7 Makumbo echirema anongoremberera; Ndizvo zvakaita chirevo mumuromo webenzi.
\v 8 Somunhu anosungira ibwe pachifuramabwe, Ndizvo zvakaita iye anokudza benzi.
\v 9 Sezvinoita minzwa muruoko rwomukariri wedoro, Ndizvo zvakaita chirevo
\ mumuromo webenzi.
