\v 7 N ose, Ndizvo zvakaita munhu
\s anosevenzesa benzi
\s neanosevenzesa vafambi.
\p
\v 11 Sembwa inodzokera kumarutsi ayo,
\s Ndizvo zvakaita benzi
\s rinopamhidza upenzi hwaro.
\p
\v 12 Unoona munhu anoti
\s ndakachenjera here?
\s Benzi riri nani kuna iye!
\p
\v 13 Simbe inoti, "Kune shumba panzira; Shumba iri munzira dzomumusha."
\p
\v 14 Gonhi rinotendereka pamahinji aro; Ndizvo zvinoita simbe panhoo dzayo.
\p
\v 15 Simbe inopinza ruoko rwayo mundiro,
\s Ino usimbe kurudzoserazve kumuromo wayo.
\p
\v 16 Simbe inozviti ndakachenjera Kupfuura vanhu vanomwe vanogona kupindura nenjere.
\p
\v 17 Somunhu anobata imbwa nenzeve dzayo,
\s ichingopfuura hayo,
\s Ndizvo zvakaita munhu anozvipinza pagakava raasina mhosva naro.
\p
\v 18 Somupengo anokanda zvitsika, Nemiseve, nezvinouraya,
\p
\v 19 Ndizvo zvinoita munhu anonyengedzera wokwake, Achiti, "Ndinongoita zvangu jee!"
\p
\v 20 Moto unodzima nokushaiwa huni; Uye kana kusina mucheri, gakava rinopera.
\p
\v 21 Sezvakaita mazimbe pazvitsika
\s zvinopfuta, nehuni pamoto,
\s Ndizvo zvakaita munhu wegakava
\s pakupfutidza rukave.
\p
\v 22 Mashoko omucheri akaita sezvimedu zvinozipa,
\s Zvinoburukira mukati-kati momuviri.
\p
\v 23 Miromo inopisa norudo pamwechete nomwoyo wakaipa,
\s Zvakafanana nomudziyo wevhu wakanamirwa
\s namarara anobva pasirivha.
\p
\v 24 Muvengi anonyengedzera nemiromo yake,
\s Asi anovanza kunyengedzera mumwoyo make.
\p
\v 25 Kana achitaura zvinonaka, usamutenda;
\s Nokuti mumwoyo make mune
\p zvinonyangadza zvinomwe.
\v 26 Kunyange kuvenga kwake
\s kuchizvivanza nokunyengedzera,
\s Kushata kwake kuchabudiswa
\s pachena pamberi peungano.
\p
\v 27 Ani naani anochera gomba, achawiramo iye;
\s Anokungurusa ibwe, richadzokera pamusoro pake.
\p
\v 28 Rurimi rwenhema runovenga akuvadzwa narwo;
\s Nomuromo unobata kumeso unoparadza.
